summary: The reputation era was an era filled with happiness, love, friendship, and taking back her life. Taylor is happier than ever,...
body: The reputation era was an era filled with happiness, love, friendship, and taking back her life. Taylor is happier than ever, she’s closer to us than ever, she found the love of her life, she broke so many records, danced all summer with us on tour, found the courage to speak up about certain topics she never did before, and showed the media and all of those who wronged her or didnt support her that she is strong, talented, fearless and that they don’t control or manage her life. Of course the album deserved more nominations, but I think I’d rather have all of that rather than another trophy. All of those things are much more valuable and beautiful❤️
